'''''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'' 2''' is the second issue of [[Star Wars Insider|''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'']], later rebranded as the ''Star Wars Insider''. Issue 2 was published in Winter [[1988]].

{{Magazine-stub|issue}}

==Contents==
===Features===
*"''Willow'': A Week On The Set Of Lucasfilm's Epic Adventure" by Robert Allan
*"''Willow'': The Novel" by [[Dan Madsen]] and John S. Davis
*"''[[Star Wars: The Role-Playing Game]]''" {{C|by Adam Schultz}}
*"Exclusive Update: ''Indiana Jones III''"
*"The Making of ''Tucker''" by [[Lisa E. Cowan]]
*"[[Star Tours: "The Ultimate Adventure" is Still the Ultimate Ride at Disneyland|''Star Tours'': 'The Ultimate Adventure' is Still the Ultimate Ride at Disneyland]]" {{C|by Lisa E. Cowan}}
*"[[Richard Marquand 1938-1987]]"

===Departments===
*"The Fan Forum"
*"[[Looking At Lucasfilm]]" {{C|by [[Robert Allan]]}}
*"[[Collections]]" {{C|by [[Adam Schultz]]}}
*"[[Inside ILM]]: Visual Effects Design" {{C|by [[John S. Davis]]}}

